.DESCRIPTION
    Functions Included:
        Confirm-Automate
        Uninstall-Automate
        Install-Automate

.LINK
    https://github.com/Braingears/PowerShell

.NOTES
    File Name      : Automate-Module.psm1
    Author         : Chuck Fowler (Chuck@Braingears.com)
    Version        : 1.0
    Creation Date  : 11/10/2019
    Purpose/Change : Initial script development
